    <h2>Quick Start</h2>                                                                               
    <p>The quickest way to get Snap is with Haskell's Cabal.  If you                                   
already have Cabal set up, then getting Snap is just two simple                                        
commands:</p>                                                                                          
    <pre>                                                                                              
      cabal update
      cabal install snap-server                                                                        
    </pre>                                                                                             
        
